With just three weeks until the November election, KING 5 wants to help you get to know your Seattle City Council candidates. 
All nine seats are up for election, as Seattle shifts to seven geographical districts and two at large seats. 
18 candidates are battling for your votes. Click on our interactive map to learn who's running and how they answered the following questions: 
1) What is your favorite part of your district? 2) How are you different and/or better for the job compared to your opponent?
